                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Flavia Severa <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XXXV <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Ulpius Bas<lb break="no" n="4"/>sus <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>IIII <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>aviae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ant</abbr><ex>oninianae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>strat</abbr><ex>or</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>iugi</abbr></expan> <supplied reason="lost">pi</supplied>en<lb break="no" n="7"/>tissim<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> po<lb break="no" n="8"/>suit <lb n="9"/>manu mea <lb n="10"/>scribsi <note>sic</note>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Stein für ein spätantikes Grab zweitverwendet. Z. 1 steht auf dem oberen Rahmen des Inschriftfeldes. (B): ILJug: Z. 5/6: leg(ionis) IIII; ILJug, Sokolovska: Z. 6: IIII Fl(aviae); Z. 7/8: pien/tissime; ILJug: Z. 10/11: mea scribsi. Datierung: Der Legionsbeiname Antoniana ist für die leg. IIII Flavia unter Septimius Severus und Caracalla sowie unter Elagabal bezeugt.</p>
            </div>
